<item>
            <title>[HIVE-28960] Compaction Stats updater does not collect column stats when hive.stats.autogather is true</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-28960</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To reproduce the issue add a test to &lt;tt&gt;TestCrudCompactorOnTez.java&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; TABLE1 = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;t1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;

  @Test
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void testMajorCompaction() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; Exception {
    executeStatementOnDriver(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;create table &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + TABLE1 + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;(a &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;, b varchar(128), c &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;) stored as orc TBLPROPERTIES (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;transactional&apos;&lt;/span&gt;=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, driver);
    executeStatementOnDriver(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;insert into &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + TABLE1 + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;(a, b, c) values (1, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;one&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, 1.1)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, driver);
    executeStatementOnDriver(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;insert into &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + TABLE1 + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;(a, b, c) values (2, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;two&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, 2.2)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, driver);

    executeStatementOnDriver(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;delete from &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + TABLE1 + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; where a = 1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, driver);

    CompactorTestUtil.runCompaction(conf, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,  TABLE1 , CompactionType.MAJOR, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;);
    CompactorTestUtil.runCleaner(conf);
    verifySuccessfulCompaction(1);

    List&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; result = execSelectAndDumpData(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;describe formatted &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + TABLE1, driver, &quot;&quot;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the &lt;tt&gt;results&lt;/tt&gt; array the string&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
	COLUMN_STATS_ACCURATE	{\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;BASIC_STATS\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;:\&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;\&quot;&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;shows that only basic stats are accurate.&lt;br/&gt;
The delete operation made the column stats stale and the stats updater running after compactor didn&apos;t collected the column stats because &lt;tt&gt;hive.stats.autogather&lt;/tt&gt; is true:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/2495898ae937de2bfd8fe72c63eec2ae905c908c/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/txn/compactor/StatsUpdater.java#L84-L88&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/hive/blob/2495898ae937de2bfd8fe72c63eec2ae905c908c/ql/src/java/org/apache/hadoop/hive/ql/txn/compactor/StatsUpdater.java#L84-L88&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
